Documentation

template<typename Result, typename Arg>
class TiledArray::Clone< Result, Arg >

Create a deep copy of a tile.

This operation creates a deep copy of a tile. The copy operation may optionally perform a clone or cast operation. If the Result and Arg types are the same, the argument tile is copied using the clone() operation is performed, otherwise the argument tile is cast to the Result type using the TiledArray::Cast<Result, Arg> functor.

Template Parameters
ResultThe result tile type
ArgumentThe argument tile type
